com.tomtom.speedtools.tilemap

Interface TileMap.ViewportTileProcessor<T>

  • Enclosing class:
    TileMap<T>

    public static interface TileMap.ViewportTileProcessor<T>
    Callback function for viewport tile processing. The template parameter T is the image class, e.g. Image or PImage.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      void process(int seqX, int seqY, TileKey tileKey, T img, int viewportX, int viewportY, int tileOffsetX, int tileOffsetY, int width, int height)
      Process one viewport tile.

    • Method Detail

      • process

        void process(int seqX,
             int seqY,
             @Nonnull
             TileKey tileKey,
             @Nullable
             T img,
             int viewportX,
             int viewportY,
             int tileOffsetX,
             int tileOffsetY,
             int width,
             int height)
        Process one viewport tile.
        Parameters:
        seqX - Sequence number in X direction (0, 1, 2, ...), 0 = left.
        seqY - Sequence number in Y direction (0, 1, 2, ...), 0 = top.
        tileKey - Tile key.
        viewportX - Position X from top-left of viewport.
        viewportY - Position Y from top-left of viewport.
        img - Tile image.
        tileOffsetX - Crop area, position X from top-left of image.
        tileOffsetY - Crop area, position Y from top-left of image.
        width - Width of crop area to plot.
        height - Height of crop area to plot.
